             was indicted for <rs id="t18060219-36-off195" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18060219-36-off195" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18060219-36-off195" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18060219-36-cd196" type="crimeDate">25th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060219-36-off195 t18060219-36-cd196"></join>, a hankerchief, value 3 s
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18060219-36-victim396" type="victimName">
                     Simon 
                     Thompson
                  <interp inst="t18060219-36-victim396" type="surname" value="Thompson"></interp>
